                "invention-title": [
                    "Ammonia fuel ship power and power generation system and working method thereof",
                    "一种氨燃料船舶动力与发电系统及其工作方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an ammonia fuel ship power and power generation system and a working method thereof, and belongs to the technical field of ammonia fuel engines. The system comprises a main engine power unit, an ammonia cracking hydrogen production unit and an auxiliary engine power generation unit, the main engine power unit is a liquid ammonia-diesel oil double direct injection engine; the auxiliary engine power generation unit comprises an ammonia-hydrogen fusion fuel engine and a power generator; the ammonia cracking hydrogen production unit comprises an ammonia gasification device, a waste gas waste heat recovery system and an ammonia cracker filled with a catalyst, and energy required by catalytic cracking is provided by cooperation of main engine power waste gas waste heat and auxiliary engine power generation heating. Ammonia fuel can be simultaneously applied to a ship main engine power generation system and an auxiliary engine power generation system, and carbon emission of a ship can be obviously reduced; meanwhile, main engine waste gas waste heat cooperates with auxiliary engine power generation heating to assist ammonia cracking hydrogen production, and therefore efficient utilization of overall energy of the system is achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种氨燃料船舶动力与发电系统及其工作方法，属于氨燃料发动机技术领域；系统包括主机动力单元、氨裂解制氢单元和辅机发电单元；主机动力单元为液氨‑柴油双直喷发动机；辅机发电单元包括氨氢融合燃料发动机和发电机；氨裂解制氢单元包括氨气化装置、废气余热回收系统及装有催化剂的氨裂解器，催化裂解所需能量由主机动力废气余热协同辅机发电加热提供。本发明实现了氨燃料在船舶主机动力和辅机发电系统上的同时应用，能够明显降低船舶碳排放；同时利用主机废气余热协同辅机发电加热辅助氨裂解制氢，从而实现了系统整体能量高效利用。"
                }
            ]
